name: H3H3 / Vape Nation vs. The Pranksters
name_original: H3H3 / Vape Nation vs. The Pranksters
description:
Join Ethan in his fight against the Pranksters! Collect sodi-pops, get helped by Papa John, stop pranksters, shoot nuclear missiles and most importantly,try to FIND ALL THE MEMES!

This game was made by a really big fan of the H3H3 youtube channel that you can find here: https://www.youtube.com/user/h3h3Productions

Probably the best Youtube channel in existence. Papa bless. Make Ethan and Hila aware of this game so they play it!

Credits: action music in the last 2 levels made by Alex Lisi
